        <Parent_String>louvers and louver components [300069721], opening components [300003138], openings and opening components [300052369], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
